Package: edr4r
Title: Client for OGC API - Environmental Data Retrieval (EDR)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Western Water Datahub", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "bwebb@lincolninst.edu")
Description: A client for OGC API - Environmental Data Retrieval (EDR)
    services, with first-class support for the Western Water Datahub
    (WWDH) deployment. Provides discovery, query, and parsing helpers
    for the locations, items, position, area, cube, radius, trajectory,
    and corridor query types. Parses CoverageJSON responses into tidy
    tibbles and GeoJSON responses into 'sf' objects.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/internetofwater/WWDH
BugReports: https://github.com/internetofwater/WWDH/issues
